    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年9月29日-2025年10月11日）",
    "followRuleId": "1290222909587562496",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1289863613818167296\">《京东开放平台大时尚品类新商激励政策》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在政策周期内，满足GMV考核目标的商家可获得广告金激励。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1290142210806145024\">《京东开放平台企业店铺&ldquo;老带新&rdquo;招商激励政策》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在政策周期内，老商家推荐新商家入驻POP-SOP模式后，新商入驻首月或下个自然月店铺维度首次达到成交单量&ge;30单或成交GMV&ge;3万元，则推荐其入驻的老商家可获得500元广告虚拟金。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1290142910080368640\">《京东开放平台个人/个体店铺&ldquo;老带新&rdquo;招商激励政策》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=882901586832134144\">《京东开放平台咚咚热情掌柜服务规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增金牌客服服务质检标准及对应的细则，并修订金牌客服认证的方式及标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1287371769056989184\">《京东开放平台五星店铺规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①认证范围剔除卖场店；②调整透标期间取消五星店铺标签展示指标；③调整五星店铺认证标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288478539486871552\">《京东开放平台经营类目规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订补充类目选择规范、类目发品阈值、类目变更、类目错挂处置等规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288761542125641728\">《京东开放平台医药和医疗保健类商品管理规则》</a>&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订细化商品发布信息等要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1287652748564762624\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11活动总则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①活动节奏：预热时间为2025年10月9日00:00:00-2025年10月9日19:59:59；正式时间为2025年10月9日20:00:00-2025年11月14日23:59:59；招商时间为2025年9月23日12:00:00-2025年11月14日23:59:59；②活动玩法：官方直降和跨店满减。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1287649847893168128\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11大促主题活动招商规则》</a>、<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288845533797310464\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11大促官方直降活动规则》</a>、<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288840126126465024\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11大促跨店满减活动规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>",
